{"article_id":"QebaexdNhbDoQXLm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"When President Donald Trump felt the need","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to lash out at Twitter on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he did n't turn to Facebook or YouTube .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"He turned to Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The president has launched any number of insults , tirades and misleading statements from his Twitter account in recent years .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"But it was two tweets","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"about voting by mail","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that spurred the company to take action ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"adding a fact check label to them .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The president fired back ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"tweeting","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that the company was `` stifling FREE SPEECH ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"by fact checking his tweets about mail-in ballots .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"But Trump 's choice of Twitter as the best platform","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"from which to attack Twitter","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"highlights the singular appeal of the platform .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"As much as the president may be angry with the company ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"there 's nothing quite like the real-time global broadcasting apparatus of Twitter , as well as the network of accounts","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that have been built up in recent years","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that amplify his statements .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"And Twitter has shown a willingness","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to let Trump test its rules","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"- including the president 's most recent attacks on MSNBC host Joe Scarborough .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` Twitter 's really the perfect platform for him , ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"said Vivian Schiller , executive director of Aspen Digital , a program of the Aspen Institute .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Schiller , the former chief digital officer of NBC News , is a former employee of Twitter .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"`` Obviously it does n't have the reach","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that Facebook does , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"`` But it has all the people","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who will amplify his message ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"be it the media or bots or other government officials . ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Just as Twitter has been opposed to booting Trump over possible violations of its terms of service ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Trump may find it difficult or impossible to divorce himself from the platform","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"that greased his path into politics .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"In the hours","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"after the conflict erupted Tuesday between Trump and Twitter ,","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"some conservatives lamented","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"that there was no way","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"the president could win","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"despite his pledge","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that he would n't allow Twitter to fact check him .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Byers Market Newsletter","depth":2},{"id":43,"text":"Get breaking news and insider analysis on the rapidly changing world of media and technology right to your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"This site is protected by recaptcha","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"`` Will Trump beat Twitter ? ''","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"asked Ali Akbar , a conservative activist","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"who also goes by the name Ali Alexander ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"from whom Twitter CEO Jack Dorsey has sought advice .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"`` The answer is hell no .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"It 's too late for spilled milk , ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"`` This issue has been completely mismanaged by both the campaign and the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"and everyone sees","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"he 's a paper tiger ''","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"- as in someone","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"who makes threats","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"but does n't follow through .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Trump and fellow Republicans have options","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to exert leverage over Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio , R-Fla. , said on Twitter","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"if the service is going to `` exercise an editorial role , ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"it should lose the special protection","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that it and other internet companies enjoy from defamation suits .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"( The Communications Decency Act of 1996 ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"often misunderstood ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"was written specifically","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"so tech companies could exercise editorial judgment . )","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Download the NBC News app for breaking news and politics","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"Trump tweeted Wednesday morning","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that `` Republicans feel","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that Social Media Platforms totally silence conservatives voices , ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"an indication","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that the president may be able to use Twitter 's fact checking efforts","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"to ramp up accusations of bias against tech companies .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` We will strongly regulate ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"or close them down ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"before we can ever allow this to happen , ''","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Trump added ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"although it 's unclear under what authority the government could do so .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"It 's far from the first time","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"politicians have sought to put pressure on tech companies over efforts","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"to rein in misinformation .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"In 2018 , lawmakers called Dorsey in front of a congressional hearing","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to answer questions","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"about how Twitter approached censorship , among other subjects .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Dorsey at the time pledged to take a light touch on most subjects","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"people tweet about .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"If the president wants to escalate the feud ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"he has few legal options ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"experts said .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` I ca n't think of any legit legal paths available here , ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"said Chip Stewart , a professor of journalism at Texas Christian University .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` The First Amendment simply bars the government from compelling a private company 's speech .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"That would literally be the censorship","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"Trump complains","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"is instead happening to him . ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Aside from extracting further promises or making regulatory threats ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"the only leverage","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Trump has","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"may be his presence .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"And he might not enjoy Facebooking , Instagramming or YouTubing as much","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"as he does tweeting .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"The president has a prodigious Facebook audience ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"even though the social network is much larger than Twitter and an important part of Trump 's re-election campaign ,","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"it does n't offer him the same instantaneous feedback of Twitter","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"because its news feed is based on a complicated algorithm .","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"Similarly , Instagram and Snapchat are n't designed for the kind of text-heavy messages","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that dominate Twitter","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"and characterize Trump 's announcements .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"YouTube requires much more camera time","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"without the benefit of instant sharing .","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"TikTok is also video-based","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"and comes with rising Republican concern about its ties to China ,","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"while fringe tech startups like Gab are relatively small .","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Using the app Nextdoor would limit the president 's reach to the neighborhoods","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"surrounding his home .","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"Twitter , likewise , has repeatedly said","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"it does n't intend to remove Trump from the service ,","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"perhaps no matter what he says .","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"It has also given him leeway with what he tweets .","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"`` We believe","depth":18},{"id":124,"text":"it 's important","depth":19},{"id":125,"text":"that the world sees how global leaders think and how they act , ''","depth":19},{"id":126,"text":"Dorsey told HuffPost last year .","depth":17},{"id":127,"text":"But now the service ,","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"by fact checking Trump for the first time ,","depth":17},{"id":129,"text":"has also drawn a line in the sand -","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"and the conflict may keep ratcheting up .","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"`` The fact","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"that they 've now applied a fact checking notice to his tweets about voting","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"means it 's going to be very hard for them not to keep labeling tweets , ''","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"said Schiller of the Aspen Institute .","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"`` They just made life much harder for themselves , honestly .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"I think","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"it 's absolutely the right decision ,","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"but it 's now much trickier . ''","depth":15}],"relations":[{"parent":277,"left":180,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":173,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":151,"right":172,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":142,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":140,"right":141,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":4,"right":145,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":9,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":10,"right":147,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":169,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":153,"right":168,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":156,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":16,"right":155,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":17,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":18,"